TOPVISION DISPLA said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 41.25% to NT$15,636,000 from NT$26,615,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             15,636           26,615    
YOY%             -41.25%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            460,702          122,554    
YOY%             275.92% 
